## 6. WP theme architecture — panhandle-theme

**One PHP rule: NEVER use the `?>` closing tag anywhere. All runner scripts ASCII-only.**

### functions.php — MUST include at top:
```php
<?php
// Suppress canonical redirect (sub-path proxy loop fix -- proven in Maryland demo)
remove_filter('template_redirect', 'redirect_canonical');
```

Then enqueue:
```php
wp_enqueue_style('google-fonts',
  'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@600;700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;600&family=Barlow:wght@500&display=swap',
  [], null);
wp_enqueue_style('panhandle-main', get_template_directory_uri() . '/assets/css/main.css', ['google-fonts'], '1.0');
wp_enqueue_script('panhandle-main', get_template_directory_uri() . '/assets/js/main.js', [], '1.0', true);
```

Register nav menus: `primary` (header), `footer-services`, `footer-cities`.

### Template files (12 files — no page builders):

| File | Route/Purpose |
|---|---|
| `front-page.php` | Homepage: hero + trust strip + 8-service grid + city coverage map + CTAs |
| `page-service.php` | Service silo — schema Service markup, FAQ section, CTA |
| `page-city.php` | City LP — geo-targeted H1, service list, bilingual note, map CTA |
| `page-commercial.php` | Commercial hub (/commercial/) |
| `page-residential.php` | Residential hub (/residential/) |
| `page-estimate.php` | CF7 estimate form |
| `page-seo-audit.php` | Free SEO Audit landing — embed + CTA to analyzer |
| `single.php` | Blog post (Article schema) |
| `page.php` | Generic fallback |
| `header.php` | Sticky nav: logo + click-to-call + "Get Estimate" orange CTA |
| `footer.php` | Address, phone, hours, service links, city links, trust badges |
| `functions.php` | (above) |

