## 10. SEO Analyzer integration (zero rebuild)

**Existing analyzer:** `https://mwegter95.github.io/free-seo-analyzer-with-js-rendering/`
**Auth endpoints (no change needed):**
- `POST api.michaelwegter.com/auth/register` — any email + 8-char password -> 201
- `POST api.michaelwegter.com/auth/login` -> JWT
- `POST api.michaelwegter.com/seo/analyze` — single-page SEO analysis (Playwright, require_auth)
- `POST api.michaelwegter.com/seo/crawl` — full-site crawl
- `GET api.michaelwegter.com/seo/crawl/stream` — SSE progress
- `GET api.michaelwegter.com/seo/reports` — saved reports list

**page-seo-audit.php content:**
```html
