## 13. Competitor gap to reinforce in copy

All major competitors (Overhead Door Co. Amarillo, Price Overhead Door, Willow Creek, Integrity Overhead Door) have ZERO city landing pages for towns outside Amarillo. Lead every city LP with:
- "Proudly serving [City] — locally owned, not a big-city company driving out"
- List of specific services relevant to that city's industry
- "Se Habla Espanol" bilingual note
- Click-to-call CTA

---

## 14. Known gotchas (do not rediscover)

1. `remove_filter('template_redirect', 'redirect_canonical')` in functions.php top — fixes infinite sub-path redirect loop (proven fix from Maryland demo)
2. NO `?>` closing tag in ANY PHP file
3. ALL runner scripts must be ASCII-only (Windows Surface charmap)
4. Docker image pull via registered service ONLY — never block in /run/exec (Cloudflare 524 at ~100s)
5. Playwright must be installed on Surface for /seo/analyze: run `python -m playwright install chromium` via runner if `playwright_available: false`
6. Bridge `accept-encoding` must be in `_HOP` set to prevent gzip corruption (already in Maryland blueprint)
7. WP siteurl and home options MUST be set to `https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/panhandle-garage-door-company` (no trailing slash) for sub-path proxy to work

